milestones.description: Dawlat Zadran and Mujeeb's 64-run partnership is AFG's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 49 between Mohammad Nabi and Aftab Alam
Taylor has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (8) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Chigumbura's 7
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Asghar Afghan's 5
